snippet.title: Rally On! | TopSpin 2K25 Official Announce Trailer | 2K
snippet.description:
TopSpin is officially back. 🎾 Step onto the virtual court and win the career Grand Slam®, compete in iconic venues, learn the game from legend John McEnroe in the TopSpin Academy, and much more.

Pre-order #TopSpin2K25 today and we’ll see you on the court April 26, 2024. Rally On!

Pre-order: https://topspin.2k.com/

Official Channels 
🎾 Instagram https://www.instagram.com/topspin2k
